Introduction

Sample overview

  • A total of 2156 features (m/z: 70.7996-1041.8419; RT: 61.0298-1078.8943) are included in the feature table.
  • A total of 15 samples with 6 groups are included in this data set.

Metabolite annotation

1. Annotation overview

  • A total of 96 features with 195 metabolites were putatively annotated by MetDNA2, covering 2 different confidence levels.

2. Initial seed annotation

  • A total of 49 feature with 84 metabolites were annotated with spectral library
  • Level 1 annotations (Exp. m/z, Exp. RT and Exp. MS/MS): 0
  • Level 2 annotations (Exp. m/z and Exp. MS/MS): 84

3. Recursive annotation

  • A total of 232 feature with 559 annotations were obtained via 15 recursive steps.
  • 66 KEGG metabolite used as seed metabolites
  • 493 known metabolites (level 3.1)
  • 0 curated unknown metabolites (level 3.2)



Figure 4. Known metabolites in recursive annotation
